* should be a class not a component
* new user on app initiate
* user will have player number
* the user class will listen to any keyboard actions made in the app
  - when there is an action it will check if it has registered action, if it does
  - send that action to the server
  - broadcast that action and that player to all players
  - all players receive that players action
  - all players fulfil that action against that player number
